<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AuraFlow AI | Next-Gen AI Automation Waitlist</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght=300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-950 text-slate-100 antialiased overflow-x-hidden">

    <nav class="border-b border-slate-800 bg-slate-950/80 backdrop-blur-md sticky top-0 z-50">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 h-16 flex items-center justify-between">
            <div class="text-xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-indigo-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                AuraFlow AI
            </div>
            <div class="hidden md:flex space-x-8 text-sm text-slate-400">
                <a href="#services" class="hover:text-white transition">Services</a>
                <a href="#features" class="hover:text-white transition">Features</a>
                <a href="#waitlist" class="hover:text-white transition">Join Waitlist</a>
            </div>
            <a href="#waitlist" class="bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-500 text-white text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition shadow-lg shadow-indigo-600/20">
                Join Waitlist
            </a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="relative py-24 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="h-[400px] w-[400px] bg-indigo-600/10 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
            <div class="h-[300px] w-[300px] bg-blue-500/10 rounded-full blur-[100px] translate-x-20"></div>
        </div>
        
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-indigo-500/10 text-indigo-400 border border-indigo-500/20 mb-6">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-indigo-400 animate-pulse"></span> Applications Open for Q3 Cohort
        </span>
        
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-tight">
            Automate Your Operations With <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 via-indigo-400 to-purple-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Custom AI Agents</span>
        </h1>
        
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            We build custom AI infrastructure, LLM integrations, and autonomous workflows. Join the waitlist to secure your deployment slot.
        </p>
        
        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="#waitlist" class="bg-slate-100 hover:bg-white text-slate-950 font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition text-center">
                Secure Your Spot
            </a>
            <a href="#services" class="border border-slate-800 hover:border-slate-700 bg-slate-900/50 text-slate-300 font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition text-center">
                Explore Services
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="border-slate-900 max-w-7xl mx-auto">

    <section id="services" class="py-20 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Our Automation Suite</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-slate-400">Tailored AI systems designed to integrate seamlessly into your existing tech stack.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 hover:border-slate-700 transition">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-blue-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-400 mb-6 font-bold text-xl">⚡</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Workflow Automation</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Connect your apps and data layers using custom AI logic to automate data entry, report generation, and multi-step manual tasks.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 hover:border-slate-700 transition">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-indigo-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-400 mb-6 font-bold text-xl">🤖</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Custom AI Agents</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Deploy smart chatbots and voice bots trained on your internal documentation to handle customer support and lead qualification 24/7.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40 hover:border-slate-700 transition">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-purple-500/10 flex items-center justify-center text-purple-400 mb-6 font-bold text-xl">📊</div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Predictive Analytics</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Extract actionable insights from raw data pipelines to predict market trends, customer churn, and operational bottlenecks.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="waitlist" class="py-20 px-6 max-w-7xl mx-auto bg-slate-900/20 border-y border-slate-900">
        <div class="text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Limited Cohort Availability</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-slate-400">To maintain build quality, we accept a limited number of scale partners each month. Join the queue to save your placeholder.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-md mx-auto grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-12 text-center">
            <div class="p-4 border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950 rounded-xl">
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo-400">14</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider mt-1">Remaining Slots</div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950 rounded-xl">
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-200">842</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider mt-1">In Queue</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto">
            <form class="space-y-4 text-left border border-slate-800 p-8 rounded-2xl bg-slate-950 shadow-xl" onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); alert('Success! You have been added to the AuraFlow AI waitlist. We will review your application within 48 hours.');">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Name</label>
                        <input type="text" required class="w-full bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg px-4 py-2.5 text-sm text-slate-100 focus:outline-none focus:border-indigo-500 transition">
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label class="block text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Work Email</label>
                        <input type="email" required class="w-full bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg px-4 py-2.5 text-sm text-slate-100 focus:outline-none focus:border-indigo-500 transition">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label class="block text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Company Website</label>
                    <input type="url" placeholder="https://example.com" required class="w-full bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg px-4 py-2.5 text-sm text-slate-100 focus:outline-none focus:border-indigo-500 transition">
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label class="block text-xs font-semibold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Primary Bottleneck to Automate</label>
                    <textarea rows="3" placeholder="Describe the manual task or workflow you need solved..." class="w-full bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 rounded-lg px-4 py-2.5 text-sm text-slate-100 focus:outline-none focus:border-indigo-500 transition"></textarea>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="w-full bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-500 text-white font-semibold py-3 rounded-lg text-sm transition shadow-lg shadow-indigo-600/20">
                    Apply For Early Access →
                </button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="border-t border-slate-900 py-8 text-center text-xs text-slate-600">
        &copy; 2026 AuraFlow AI. All rights reserved. Built with precision.
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
